body:
My friends and I had this idea for a skin for our boy, Bard {{champion:432}} 
So we were thinking about new skins and we thought: Pizza Man Bard.
He could be wearing a pizza delivery boy outfit and his W could be a single pizza slice, that slowly turns into a whole pizza. His chimes could be bottles of soda and his meeps could be little pizza delivery boys. His dash homeguard thing could be him riding on a scooter, similar to PROJECT: Vayne {{champion:67}} 
What do you guys think??
